=========================
Installing PyKst
=========================


Requirements
------------

	Python 3.6 or higher
	NumPy
	PyQt5
	KST 2.x plotting application


Installing
----------

	pip install numpy PyQt5
	pip install .


Configuring KST2 executable
----------------------------

	Set KST2 environment variable or add kst2 to system PATH.

	Windows:
		set KST2=C:\path\to\kst2.exe

	Linux/Unix:
		export KST2=/path/to/kst2

